id: pm-cxdg
title: Configurable semantic corpus character limit (search.embedding_corpus_max_characters)
description: "Corpus truncation (8000 default, 3200 Ollama) is hardcoded in corpus.ts; large-body items truncate with no override and cost-sensitive users cannot lower it. buildSemanticCorpusInput already accepts maxCharacters."
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 3
