  "2026-06-06T06:19:17.624Z",codex-search-bundle,"Implemented optional search.embedding_corpus_max_characters setting across type/validator/store/config alias surfaces; semantic corpus builders in reindex + mutation refresh now resolve provider defaults (8000 openai-compatible / 3200 ollama) when unset and emit search_embedding_corpus_max_characters_invalid:using_provider_default on invalid configured values. Added deterministic coverage for override + fallback behavior in corpus/reindex/cache/config tests; docs updated in CONFIGURATION/PRD/README. Verification: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/search-corpus.spec.ts tests/unit/reindex-command.spec.ts tests/unit/search-cache.spec.ts tests/unit/config-key-aliases-search.spec.ts tests/unit/nested-settings.spec.ts; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage."
